# KIT_Contest 저장소 전체 — 비밀·로컬·캐시 제외

# --- OS / 편집기 ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# --- Python (전체 하위 경로) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/$py.class
**/.Python
**/*.so
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/.eggs/
**/*.egg-info/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
**/*.cover

# --- 환경 변수·비밀 (예시 파일은 커밋 가능) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.sample

# --- Streamlit ---
**/.streamlit/secrets.toml
**/.streamlit/secrets.local.toml

# --- Google / Firebase / GCP 자격 증명 ---
**/*firebase-adminsdk*.json
**/*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
**/firebase-service-account.json
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
**/application_default_credentials.json
**/gcloud-application-credentials.json

# --- 로컬 데이터 (Chroma 등) ---
**/chroma_data/*
!**/chroma_data/.gitkeep

# --- 로그·임시 ---
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/.cache/
**/tmp/
**/temp/

# --- Jupyter ---
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Node (향후 도입 시) ---
**/node_modules/
